data.description: Immaculate and spacious 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home, perfect for comfortable living. Enjoy the cozy ambiance of a gas fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Discover the spot ready for a hot tub, allowing you to relax and unwind in your private oasis. Take pleasure in a large screened-in porch, providing an ideal space for entertaining or simply enjoying the outdoors. Built in cabinetry throughout adds both beauty and functionality to the home, providing ample storage options. Privacy fenced yard offering a tranquil setting for outdoor activities. 2-car garage with ample space for parking and storage. With over 3600 square feet of total living area, this home provides plenty of room for relaxation, work, and play. Don't miss the chance to make this your dream home, schedule your showing today though showing time!
